1
00:00:21,070 --> 00:00:24,180
♪The breeze of the 1990s drifts by♪

2
00:00:24,350 --> 00:00:27,180
♪Memories slowly flicker past♪

3
00:00:27,650 --> 00:00:31,430
♪My heartbeat
rises and falls with the tune♪

4
00:00:31,500 --> 00:00:34,580
♪The story quietly begins here♪

5
00:00:35,330 --> 00:00:38,640
♪Under the dim lights, our eyes meet♪

6
00:00:38,710 --> 00:00:41,850
♪Time seems to stand still♪

7
00:00:42,350 --> 00:00:45,990
♪Your smile
breaks through the clouds like sun♪

8
00:00:46,060 --> 00:00:49,150
♪Melting the snow deep in my heart♪

9
00:00:49,580 --> 00:00:53,090
♪Street posters spread signals of love♪

10
00:00:53,150 --> 00:00:56,110
♪Our story slowly begins to ferment♪

11
00:00:56,800 --> 00:01:00,730
♪Hand in hand,
going through every dusk corner♪

12
00:01:00,930 --> 00:01:04,800
♪The taste of happiness is so subtle♪

13
00:01:05,480 --> 00:01:08,740
♪Crossing back to the 1990s stage♪

14
00:01:09,150 --> 00:01:12,480
♪You're my most beautiful surprise♪

15
00:01:12,790 --> 00:01:16,210
♪Love's flame burns within my heart♪

16
00:01:16,680 --> 00:01:19,710
♪Not afraid of obstacles ahead♪

17
00:01:20,180 --> 00:01:23,560
♪Sway with the rhythm.
Feel your heart pound♪

18
00:01:23,660 --> 00:01:27,150
♪This love will never change♪

19
00:01:27,950 --> 00:01:35,080
♪We hold tight in this crazy era♪

20
00:01:35,160 --> 00:01:40,060
♪1990s love is what we rely on♪

21
00:01:40,100 --> 00:01:42,070
=Once More Love in 1995=

22
00:01:42,260 --> 00:01:44,987
=Episode 12=

23
00:01:59,319 --> 00:02:00,280
Still laughing?

24
00:02:01,439 --> 00:02:03,280
Can you stop being so impulsive?

25
00:02:04,675 --> 00:02:05,475
What's wrong?

26
00:02:06,500 --> 00:02:07,661
With the situation earlier,

27
00:02:07,937 --> 00:02:09,599
what if Zhou Zeyang panicked?

28
00:02:13,987 --> 00:02:16,199
You're usually so serious,

29
00:02:16,562 --> 00:02:17,950
I didn't expect you to care.

30
00:02:19,750 --> 00:02:20,550
Zhuang Yan.

31
00:02:20,912 --> 00:02:22,231
Are you complimenting me?

32
00:02:37,887 --> 00:02:39,670
Zhou Zeyang,
how dare you show your face here?

33
00:02:40,100 --> 00:02:41,000
Ms. Zhuang.

34
00:02:41,137 --> 00:02:41,857
I...

35
00:02:43,562 --> 00:02:44,683
Why did you hit him again?

36
00:02:45,137 --> 00:02:45,639
Zhuang Yan.

37
00:02:45,960 --> 00:02:47,280
What did Zeyang do to offend you?

38
00:02:47,280 --> 00:02:48,280
I hit him.

39
00:02:50,610 --> 00:02:52,390
Everyone must take responsibility
for their actions.

40
00:02:52,525 --> 00:02:53,765
I hit Zhou Zeyang.

41
00:02:54,037 --> 00:02:55,197
Nothing wrong with admitting it.

42
00:02:56,737 --> 00:02:57,497
Mr. Qin.

43
00:02:58,080 --> 00:02:59,280
Given your character,

44
00:02:59,280 --> 00:03:00,759
you have no reason to hit anyone.

45
00:03:01,250 --> 00:03:02,850
I already have a lead on the attacker.

46
00:03:03,400 --> 00:03:04,971
I'll report it to the police tomorrow.

47
00:03:05,212 --> 00:03:06,011
A lead?

48
00:03:09,879 --> 00:03:10,840
I brought you

49
00:03:11,080 --> 00:03:12,680
this scarf from abroad.

50
00:03:14,350 --> 00:03:14,957
Shanshan.

51
00:03:15,187 --> 00:03:16,267
It's not what you think.

52
00:03:16,267 --> 00:03:16,786
Yes.

53
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:18,727
The scarf is mine.

54
00:03:19,210 --> 00:03:20,280
Nothing wrong with admitting it.

55
00:03:21,162 --> 00:03:22,002
Zhou Zeyang.

56
00:03:22,937 --> 00:03:23,898
If you're a man,

57
00:03:23,898 --> 00:03:26,138
repeat what you said about Shanshan

58
00:03:26,138 --> 00:03:27,337
behind her back today.

59
00:03:28,462 --> 00:03:29,582
If you dare repeat it,

60
00:03:29,582 --> 00:03:31,103
I'll go to the police station with you.

61
00:03:32,837 --> 00:03:33,587
Shanshan.

62
00:03:33,887 --> 00:03:35,887
Is there some misunderstanding here?

63
00:03:36,687 --> 00:03:37,400
How about

64
00:03:37,879 --> 00:03:38,840
you two talk first?

65
00:03:39,125 --> 00:03:40,126
I'll step aside first.

66
00:03:40,450 --> 00:03:42,595
Zhou Zeyang, how long
are you going to deceive Shanshan?

67
00:03:43,300 --> 00:03:45,159
I thought you were just a simple jerk.

68
00:03:45,250 --> 00:03:46,887
I didn't expect you
to be shameless to the core.

69
00:03:48,425 --> 00:03:49,665
Don't you just want to pin it on me?

70
00:03:50,475 --> 00:03:51,402
I admit my crime.

71
00:03:51,800 --> 00:03:52,960
Dare you admit what's yours?

72
00:03:53,987 --> 00:03:55,666
He didn't accuse anyone.

73
00:03:57,212 --> 00:03:58,051
Oh.

74
00:03:58,862 --> 00:04:00,327
You sly jerk.

75
00:04:00,879 --> 00:04:02,159
Here it is.

76
00:04:02,759 --> 00:04:04,639
So why exactly did you hit him?

77
00:04:04,639 --> 00:04:06,039
Because he proposed to me.

78
00:04:06,039 --> 00:04:07,719
You beat him up?

79
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:10,679
Shanshan.

80
00:04:10,919 --> 00:04:12,520
Zhou Zeyang isn't a good person.

81
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:14,700
He's been cheating behind your back.

82
00:04:14,762 --> 00:04:16,003
He doesn't love you at all.

83
00:04:16,003 --> 00:04:17,243
Stop talking.

84
00:04:21,175 --> 00:04:22,855
How can you say that?

85
00:04:23,537 --> 00:04:25,498
I know you dislike Zhou Zeyang,

86
00:04:26,100 --> 00:04:28,040
but I refuse to believe you did this.

87
00:04:28,279 --> 00:04:29,000
Shanshan.

88
00:04:29,279 --> 00:04:31,160
This is far more complicated
than you think.

89
00:04:31,160 --> 00:04:32,360
You're saying

90
00:04:32,600 --> 00:04:34,879
Zhou Zeyang proposed to me
because of Jinxin?

91
00:04:35,087 --> 00:04:37,200
Hitting him was for my own good, right?

92
00:04:38,287 --> 00:04:40,088
But I know Zeyang better than you.

93
00:04:40,225 --> 00:04:41,506
I trust him.

94
00:04:41,762 --> 00:04:43,322
I will marry him.

95
00:04:43,637 --> 00:04:44,887
If you insist on opposing,

96
00:04:45,050 --> 00:04:46,830
there's no need
to make things difficult for each other.

97
00:04:59,200 --> 00:05:00,040
Don't go after them.

98
00:05:00,450 --> 00:05:01,931
It's because
I've done a lot of bad things

99
00:05:01,931 --> 00:05:03,251
that she won't believe me.

100
00:05:14,319 --> 00:05:15,560
Qin Jiamin, are you on the wrong meds?

101
00:05:15,560 --> 00:05:16,759
I took the wrong meds?

102
00:05:16,759 --> 00:05:17,825
I haven't even asked
why you're acting insane

103
00:05:17,825 --> 00:05:19,426
that you beat Zhou Zeyang like that.

104
00:05:19,637 --> 00:05:20,996
Do you have any respect for the law?

105
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:22,425
Do you think Haicheng
is your hometown village,

106
00:05:22,425 --> 00:05:23,785
where you can do whatever you want?

107
00:05:24,137 --> 00:05:26,199
Zhou Zeyang is unbelievable.

108
00:05:26,587 --> 00:05:27,828
He got hit by a woman

109
00:05:27,828 --> 00:05:30,120
and is eager to announce it
to the whole world.

110
00:05:30,912 --> 00:05:32,439
First he complained to Shanshan,

111
00:05:32,439 --> 00:05:33,800
and now he's clinging to you.

112
00:05:35,250 --> 00:05:36,930
Is he your boyfriend or your son?

113
00:05:37,287 --> 00:05:38,560
Does he call you "mom"?

114
00:05:39,240 --> 00:05:39,879
Zhuang Yan.

115
00:05:40,120 --> 00:05:41,759
I've only been holding back

116
00:05:41,759 --> 00:05:42,900
for my brother's sake.

117
00:05:43,040 --> 00:05:44,537
You really think
I wouldn't call the police?

118
00:05:44,639 --> 00:05:46,759
If you have any shame,
leave on your own.

119
00:05:46,759 --> 00:05:48,319
Otherwise,
I'll have security escort you out.

120
00:05:49,375 --> 00:05:50,176
Stop making a scene.

121
00:05:51,262 --> 00:05:52,702
Many people are watching.

122
00:05:53,050 --> 00:05:54,651
Do you want to get fired?

123
00:05:55,040 --> 00:05:55,759
Mo.

124
00:05:55,759 --> 00:05:57,360
Why are you defending her again?

125
00:05:57,399 --> 00:05:58,600
How long are you going

126
00:05:58,600 --> 00:05:59,825
to let this woman bully me?

127
00:05:59,879 --> 00:06:01,319
When has Zhuang Yan ever bullied you?

128
00:06:01,879 --> 00:06:02,800
All this time,

129
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:04,800
haven't you been leading others
to isolate her,

130
00:06:04,879 --> 00:06:06,562
exclude her, and pick on her?

131
00:06:06,612 --> 00:06:09,525
She beat Zhou Zeyang up, didn't you see?

132
00:06:09,525 --> 00:06:11,279
The one who got beaten was Zhou Zeyang.

133
00:06:11,362 --> 00:06:13,081
Who you like is your business,

134
00:06:13,081 --> 00:06:14,837
but can you think a little
before you act?

135
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:16,500
Stop letting people use you every time.

136
00:06:17,680 --> 00:06:19,000
I get it now.

137
00:06:19,079 --> 00:06:21,425
So no matter
what lawless things Zhuang Yan does,

138
00:06:21,425 --> 00:06:22,866
you'll cover for her, right?

139
00:06:22,962 --> 00:06:25,243
You dislike Zhou Zeyang
and don't care if he lives or dies,

140
00:06:25,243 --> 00:06:25,900
fine.

141
00:06:26,037 --> 00:06:28,016
What about me?
Do you still see me as your sister?

142
00:06:28,439 --> 00:06:29,240
Qin Jiamin.

143
00:06:29,800 --> 00:06:32,812
Look at what you've become
after fooling around with Zhou Zeyang.

144
00:06:34,700 --> 00:06:37,278
He easily made you panic
with just a few sweet words.

145
00:06:37,462 --> 00:06:38,879
Don't you find yourself ridiculous?

146
00:06:39,800 --> 00:06:40,680
I'm telling you.

147
00:06:41,575 --> 00:06:43,392
Keep your distance from Zhou Zeyang.

148
00:06:43,925 --> 00:06:45,324
If you're still with him,

149
00:06:45,879 --> 00:06:47,800
don't blame me
for cutting you off as my sister.

150
00:06:47,879 --> 00:06:48,920
Qin Mo, you're disregarding

151
00:06:48,920 --> 00:06:50,120
your own sister for this woman?

152
00:06:50,120 --> 00:06:51,120
Do you like her that much?

153
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:52,160
Yes.

154
00:07:24,325 --> 00:07:28,075
(Newspapers,
Magazines, Long-Distance Calls)

155
00:07:44,639 --> 00:07:45,600
Can you step aside?

156
00:07:48,360 --> 00:07:49,480
I'm worried about you.

157
00:07:49,862 --> 00:07:50,862
Thanks.

158
00:07:51,480 --> 00:07:53,800
Thanks for haunting me like a plague.

159
00:07:53,959 --> 00:07:56,680
Thanks for bringing me endless trouble,

160
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:58,399
making every day a disaster
from the moment I wake up.

161
00:08:02,240 --> 00:08:03,000
Zhuang Yan.

162
00:08:04,199 --> 00:08:05,480
Is my concern for you

163
00:08:06,560 --> 00:08:08,000
really just a burden?

164
00:08:09,160 --> 00:08:10,160
Is it not?

165
00:08:10,959 --> 00:08:12,639
I only have Shanshan here.

166
00:08:12,875 --> 00:08:13,689
But now,

167
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:15,879
I've not only lost her trust,

168
00:08:15,975 --> 00:08:17,896
but I've also pushed her
toward Zhou Zeyang.

169
00:08:30,720 --> 00:08:32,559
Even though I don't understand
what you're saying,

170
00:08:32,762 --> 00:08:34,072
I sincerely apologize.

171
00:08:38,039 --> 00:08:38,960
I'm sorry.

172
00:08:52,399 --> 00:08:53,279
Jiamin.

173
00:08:54,200 --> 00:08:55,287
We're still at the office.

174
00:08:55,337 --> 00:08:57,320
I don't care. I miss you.

175
00:09:05,639 --> 00:09:08,279
Look at how much
you've suffered recently.

176
00:09:08,799 --> 00:09:10,879
Why don't you break up
with Zhuang Shanshan already?

177
00:09:11,240 --> 00:09:12,720
How long are you going to keep this up?

178
00:09:14,360 --> 00:09:15,679
Not yet.

179
00:09:16,360 --> 00:09:18,240
If I break up with her now,

180
00:09:18,600 --> 00:09:20,600
you'll still be labeled a homewrecker.

181
00:09:21,399 --> 00:09:23,279
I don't want to see anyone slander you.

182
00:09:24,000 --> 00:09:25,200
Give me a little more time.

183
00:09:25,519 --> 00:09:26,799
I'll handle it properly.

184
00:09:27,360 --> 00:09:28,159
Huh?

185
00:09:28,337 --> 00:09:29,538
Zhou Zeyang.

186
00:09:30,080 --> 00:09:32,039
You're not just stalling to fool me,
are you?

187
00:09:32,639 --> 00:09:34,080
Do you expect me
to wait for you my whole life?

188
00:09:45,159 --> 00:09:46,840
Don't worry, baby.

189
00:09:48,080 --> 00:09:49,787
Zhuang Yan won't be proud for long.

190
00:09:52,360 --> 00:09:55,399
I'll cut ties
with Zhuang Shanshan by then.

191
00:10:08,399 --> 00:10:09,240
Shanshan.

192
00:10:14,759 --> 00:10:15,799
Mr. Qin.

193
00:10:15,799 --> 00:10:16,600
Mo.

194
00:10:17,799 --> 00:10:18,120
Mr. Qin.

195
00:10:18,679 --> 00:10:19,519
Mo!

196
00:10:22,950 --> 00:10:25,200
I threw this punch for Shanshan.

197
00:10:25,562 --> 00:10:26,399
Mr. Qin.

198
00:10:27,039 --> 00:10:28,159
I truly like Jiamin.

199
00:10:28,159 --> 00:10:29,120
Truly?

200
00:10:30,919 --> 00:10:31,840
Stop hitting him.

201
00:10:34,600 --> 00:10:35,039
I threw

202
00:10:36,320 --> 00:10:38,200
this punch as Jiamin's elder brother.

203
00:10:39,639 --> 00:10:40,840
From today on,

204
00:10:41,200 --> 00:10:42,279
get out of Jinxin.

205
00:10:43,080 --> 00:10:44,279
Don't let me see you again.

206
00:11:29,679 --> 00:11:30,519
Shanshan.

207
00:11:31,519 --> 00:11:33,600
I know you're still mad at me.

208
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:35,799
What's between Qin Jiamin and me
isn't what you think.

209
00:11:35,919 --> 00:11:37,519
Zhou Zeyang, stop pretending.

210
00:11:38,120 --> 00:11:39,519
I was foolish before,

211
00:11:39,520 --> 00:11:41,039
mistaking false feelings
for genuine ones,

212
00:11:41,039 --> 00:11:42,960
and spoke harshly
to the ones who truly loved me.

213
00:11:50,879 --> 00:11:52,000
Here's your ring back.

214
00:11:52,399 --> 00:11:53,320
Let's end it here.

215
00:11:53,879 --> 00:11:55,679
I don't want everyone
to suffer with you.

216
00:11:56,387 --> 00:11:57,100
Shanshan.

217
00:11:58,000 --> 00:11:59,320
I was wrong.

218
00:11:59,399 --> 00:11:59,799
I was wrong.

219
00:12:00,519 --> 00:12:01,840
We've been together so long.

220
00:12:02,120 --> 00:12:03,320
Will you give me another chance?

221
00:12:03,679 --> 00:12:06,039
I can cut all ties with Qin Jiamin.

222
00:12:06,480 --> 00:12:08,200
Just forgive me, okay?

223
00:12:08,399 --> 00:12:10,480
I promise
I won't make the same mistake again.

224
00:12:10,480 --> 00:12:11,799
Shanshan, I'm begging you.

225
00:12:11,799 --> 00:12:12,639
I can't live without you.

226
00:12:12,639 --> 00:12:13,399
Shanshan.

227
00:12:14,250 --> 00:12:15,050
Shanshan.

228
00:12:19,162 --> 00:12:20,402
Cut all ties.

229
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:21,880
Can't live without me?

230
00:12:24,840 --> 00:12:26,279
I'm just a tool you use

231
00:12:26,279 --> 00:12:27,840
against Qin and Zhuang Yan.

232
00:12:28,559 --> 00:12:30,919
Qin might waver because of Jiamin.

233
00:12:31,480 --> 00:12:33,279
But as long as I still like you,

234
00:12:33,720 --> 00:12:35,840
Yan will never be able
to do anything to you.

235
00:12:36,039 --> 00:12:36,919
Am I right?

236
00:12:52,399 --> 00:12:53,200
Shanshan.

237
00:12:55,519 --> 00:12:56,480
Zhou Zeyang.

238
00:12:56,750 --> 00:12:58,093
Let's end this here.

239
00:12:58,550 --> 00:12:59,749
Stop bothering me.

240
00:13:16,159 --> 00:13:17,840
Shanshan!

241
00:13:23,720 --> 00:13:24,440
Don't worry.

242
00:13:24,759 --> 00:13:25,879
Shanshan will be fine.

243
00:13:25,919 --> 00:13:27,720
Maybe she just wants
to find a place to calm down.

244
00:13:29,399 --> 00:13:30,519
It's all my fault.

245
00:13:32,200 --> 00:13:33,399
She depends on Zhou Zeyang so much,

246
00:13:33,399 --> 00:13:34,759
yet I still pushed her so hard.

247
00:13:35,200 --> 00:13:36,087
It's all my fault.

248
00:13:36,480 --> 00:13:37,679
How can this be your fault?

249
00:13:37,679 --> 00:13:39,200
You didn't know what would happen.

250
00:13:40,000 --> 00:13:41,279
You don't understand.

251
00:13:41,840 --> 00:13:44,559
Shanshan is the sole reason I'm here.

252
00:13:44,840 --> 00:13:46,039
If anything happens to her,

253
00:13:46,039 --> 00:13:48,480
I will never forgive myself.

254
00:13:50,399 --> 00:13:53,000
Even though she's not my biological...

255
00:13:56,399 --> 00:13:57,679
biological sister,

256
00:13:59,480 --> 00:14:01,279
protecting her is still my duty.

257
00:14:08,320 --> 00:14:09,039
Zhuang Yan.

258
00:14:09,320 --> 00:14:09,919
Look.

259
00:14:10,399 --> 00:14:11,480
Shanshan.

260
00:14:14,125 --> 00:14:17,800
♪But that orange soda you chose♪

261
00:14:17,800 --> 00:14:19,280
(Yan probably)

262
00:14:19,712 --> 00:14:21,472
(doesn't want to talk to me now.)

263
00:14:22,275 --> 00:14:23,995
(She always thought of me.)

264
00:14:25,212 --> 00:14:26,732
(I still hurt her.)

265
00:14:27,712 --> 00:14:34,700
♪Time borrowed,
secretly returned to you♪

266
00:14:35,337 --> 00:14:40,787
♪Shopping for groceries with you,
going through the noisy market♪

267
00:14:42,475 --> 00:14:48,575
♪Listening to you complain
that winter melon costs more now♪

268
00:14:51,200 --> 00:14:53,159
- Shanshan.
- Shanshan!

269
00:14:56,350 --> 00:15:03,650
♪Time borrowed, closely following you♪

270
00:15:03,862 --> 00:15:09,550
♪Watching needles
weave through the afternoon♪

271
00:15:10,525 --> 00:15:16,912
♪The fine hair at your temples
glow like honey♪

272
00:15:19,200 --> 00:15:21,559
It's my fault
for not protecting you well.

273
00:15:25,387 --> 00:15:29,412
♪That blue bedsheet drying in the wind♪

274
00:15:46,600 --> 00:15:50,238
♪The old dial tone circles in my ear♪

275
00:15:50,363 --> 00:15:53,675
♪Faded tickets point to a cicada summer♪

276
00:15:53,838 --> 00:15:57,425
♪The videotape
whispers your image in the frame♪

277
00:15:57,725 --> 00:16:01,013
♪Against the light, the plaid shirt
reveals a clear and transparent smile♪

278
00:16:01,238 --> 00:16:04,863
♪I'm a clumsy guest in a frozen scene♪

279
00:16:05,025 --> 00:16:08,363
♪How do I answer familiar lines?♪

280
00:16:08,438 --> 00:16:12,150
♪I know
the train will leave this station♪

281
00:16:12,200 --> 00:16:16,063
♪I know the ending's in a faded future♪

282
00:16:16,125 --> 00:16:22,175
♪Yet I want to approach that warmth♪

283
00:16:23,350 --> 00:16:30,088
♪Even one second rewrites missed lines♪

284
00:16:30,375 --> 00:16:34,650
♪Rewind to 1995,
back to the street we met♪

285
00:16:34,650 --> 00:16:37,950
♪Wind blows through the sycamore leaves
and lands on your shoulder♪

286
00:16:38,025 --> 00:16:42,325
♪I wish I could pause and stop time♪

287
00:16:42,388 --> 00:16:46,038
♪Let unspoken love
be preserved forever as amber♪

288
00:16:46,038 --> 00:16:49,600
♪Rewind to 1995,
gentle touch of fingertips♪

289
00:16:49,650 --> 00:16:52,913
♪Star sparks in your eyes burn my chest♪

290
00:16:52,913 --> 00:16:56,663
♪This looping script
is beyond my saving♪

291
00:16:56,663 --> 00:17:03,375
♪I can only stay with you till the end
in this inverted hourglass♪
